disruptions.title: Flinders Street Station: Temporary pedestrian access changes from Saturday 30 April 2022 to 2024
disruptions.description: Flinders Street Station will be affected by pedestrian access changes from Saturday 30 April 2022 to 2024, due to station precinct works.

disruptions.title: Bayswater Station: Temporary car park closure until July 2024
disruptions.description: Up to 30 car park spaces are temporarily closed in sections of the Bayswater Station car park, due to project works.
